txt.en: Ylgraf can be found on the northern edge of the Beorning-lands.\n\nYou should defeat wargs and burn animal carcasses found at Ylgraf.

Wargs from the north have made a hiding-place among the rocks at Ylgraf in the Beorning-lands. These beasts from Gundabad will be a danger to the peaceful folk of the vales and should be dealt with immediately.

You defeated many wargs at Ylgraf and destroyed their food, sending the creatures of Gundabad a message that they are unwelcome among the Vales of Anduin. The folk of the Beorning-lands are safer now for your efforts here.
Ylgraf can be found on the northern edge of the Beorning-lands.\n\nYou should defeat wargs and burn animal carcasses found at Ylgraf.

Wargs from the north hide in the far reaches of the Beorning-lands.
